lead_paragraph: Steven Gerrard missed an early penalty but capped Los Angeles Galaxy's 5-2 win over Real Salt Lake with a stoppage-time goal in Major League Soccer on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Gerrard Misses Early Penalty, Scores Late as Galaxy Beat RSL
